<view class="container">
  <view class="section-title">图片压缩</view>

  <view class="card">
    <file-picker
      file="{{selectedFile}}"
      accept="image"
      title="选择图片"
      description="支持 JPG、PNG、WebP 格式"
      bind:selected="handleFileSelected"
    />

    <view class="config-area" wx:if="{{selectedFile}}">
      <view class="config-item">
        <view class="config-label">压缩质量: {{quality}}%</view>
        <slider
          min="10"
          max="100"
          value="{{quality}}"
          show-value
          activeColor="#07c160"
          bindchanging="handleQualityChanging"
          bindchange="handleQualityChange"
        />
      </view>

      <view class="estimate-box" wx:if="{{estimatedSizeText}}">
        <view class="estimate-title">压缩结果预估（仅供参考）</view>
        <view class="estimate-row">原图大小：{{originalSizeText}}</view>
        <view class="estimate-row">预计大小：{{estimatedSizeText}}</view>
        <view class="estimate-row">预计减少：{{estimatedReduceText}}</view>
      </view>

      <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="handleSubmit">开始压缩</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tips-card">
    <view class="tips-title">使用提示</view>
    <view class="tips-item">1. 质量越低，文件越小，但图片会越模糊</view>
    <view class="tips-item">2. 建议质量设置在 60%-80% 之间以平衡大小和清晰度</view>
    <view class="tips-item">3. 预估值会受图片内容和格式影响，实际结果可能略有差异</view>
  </view>
</view>
